document_data.mainbody:
Wyrekka Kusell was a bard famous in the eastern Sea of Fallen Stars and the regional agent of the Moonstars for Thesk, Impiltur, Narfell and Great Dale in the Year of the Tankard, 1370 DR.
Wyrekka made her home in Telflamm when she wasnt wandering Thesk, Impiltur, and the Great Dale.
